channel.title: UNSHACKLED! Daily Devotionals
channel.itunes:author: UNSHACKLED! - Pacific Garden Mission
channel.itunes:summary: These bite-sized episodes, built on real-life accounts, help us ponder the application of Scripture to our lives. Each devotional tells a dramatic testimony of transformation while addressing a relatable issue of the human condition. A key Bible verse is provided, so the listener can dig deeper into its specific intent and what it means for our lives, in these UNSHACKLED! Daily Devotionals.
